sections.Trivia:
- The first part of the episode had one of the trucks of Cheetah Delivery Service appear.
- The police car outside is a Toyota Crown Sedan [S200] 2012. The license plate number is 新宿 800, は 23-86 (Shinjuku 800, Ha 23-86).
- The suspects are named after food on a Café Menu[1]:
- Daiki Saraie (更家 大輝) is named after salad (サラダ, sarada);
- Toshinori Motosu (本巣 利範) is named after toasts (トースト, tōsuto);
- Isuzu Naomura (直村 伊鈴) is named after omurice (オムライス, omuraisu), a dish of rice wrapped in scrambled eggs popular in Japanese restaurants;
- Tamao Hasunuma (蓮沼 珠央) is named after pasta (パスタ, pasuta).
